CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1783874992
OL,3,COne side as 'guilty as the other' says
OL,4,Cson of man murdered by IRA informants
OL,6,FUTV can exclusively reveal the
OL,7,Fgovernment is to pay out up to ten
OL,8,Fmillion pounds to dozens of families
OL,9,Fwhose loved ones were murdered,
OL,10,Ftortured and terrorised by a notorious
OL,11,FIRA unit riddled with state informants.
OL,13,FFrank Hegarty was discovered dumped on
OL,14,Fthe side of a border road in Co Tyrone
OL,15,Fin May 1986.
OL,17,FThe 45-year-old had been shot in the
OL,18,Fhead with his hands bound and his eyes
OL,19,Ftaped shut.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/9
