PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1783874992
OL,3,COne side as 'guilty as the other' says
OL,4,Cson of man murdered by IRA informants
OL,6,FThe IRA man was suspected of betraying
OL,7,Frepublican secrets to the state.
OL,9,FFrank's son Ryan Hegarty rarely speaks
OL,10,Fpublicly but on Friday he told UTV:
OL,11,F"Seen it on the news.
OL,13,F"I recognised his clothes. And I says,
OL,14,F'That's my daddy.'
OL,16,F"It was my daddy, because I seen him
OL,17,Fin them clothes. The last time I seen
OL,18,Fhim alive, he was wearing the same
OL,19,Fclothes."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1783874992
OL,3,COne side as 'guilty as the other' says
OL,4,Cson of man murdered by IRA informants
OL,6,FHe continued: "They have called me
OL,7,Ftout, they have called me a MI5 agent.
OL,9,F"I was five years of age when this
OL,10,Fhappened. I'm totally innocent,
OL,11,Fabsolutely innocent.
OL,13,F"I have absolutely nothing to do...
OL,14,Fjust because I'm my father's son.
OL,16,F"This ideology they're putting across
OL,17,Fthat this was a romantic war,
OL,18,Fabsolutely not. That is not the case."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
