PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1783874992
OL,3,COne side as 'guilty as the other' says
OL,4,Cson of man murdered by IRA informants
OL,6,FFor decades Hegarty's abduction and
OL,7,Fmurder was linked to army agent
OL,8,Fcodenamed Stakeknife.
OL,10,FWhile never officially identified, the
OL,11,Frepublican Freddie Scappaticci was
OL,12,Fwidely believed to be the agent
OL,13,Fdespite his denials.
OL,15,FOperation Kenova investigated
OL,16,FStakeknife linking him to 14
OL,17,Fexecutions alongside a catalogue of
OL,18,Fother crimes.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1783874992
OL,3,COne side as 'guilty as the other' says
OL,4,Cson of man murdered by IRA informants
OL,6,FScappaticci's rise through the ranks
OL,7,Fof the IRA saw him tasked with hunting
OL,8,Fdown informants with the much-feared
OL,9,F'internal security unit', nicknamed
OL,10,Fthe 'nutting squad'.
OL,12,FBut we now know he was the biggest spy
OL,13,Fof them all, while lives were
OL,14,Fsacrificed to protect this highly
OL,15,Fvalued asset.
OL,17,FIt has now been revealed, he was not
OL,18,Finvolved in Hegarty's death.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
