PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1783874992
OL,3,COne side as 'guilty as the other' says
OL,4,Cson of man murdered by IRA informants
OL,6,FHegarty's killer was another informant
OL,7,Fwithin the IRA's internal security
OL,8,Funit.
OL,10,FThis case became even more infamous
OL,11,Fwhen it was claimed Martin McGuinness
OL,12,Flured Frank Hegarty out of hiding in
OL,13,FEngland and to his death.
OL,15,FThis claim was strenuously denied by
OL,16,Fthe former deputy first minister right
OL,17,Fup until his death.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1783874992
OL,3,COne side as 'guilty as the other' says
OL,4,Cson of man murdered by IRA informants
OL,6,FUTV understands the settlement between
OL,7,Fthe state and families reflects that
OL,8,Fthere were other spies among those
OL,9,Franks involved in the killings,
OL,10,Ftorture and treachery.
OL,12,FKevin Winters who represents the
OL,13,Ffamilies said: "I think this is a very
OL,14,Fsignificant day, in fact that we see a
OL,15,Fraft of cases that have nothing to do
OL,16,Fwith Freddie Scappaticci, that are now
OL,17,Fbeing settled by the British
OL,18,Fgovernment."
OL,20,FFor Ryan Hegarty, this was never about
OL,21,Fmoney.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
