PN,41608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1783874992
OL,3,COne side as 'guilty as the other' says
OL,4,Cson of man murdered by IRA informants
OL,6,FAlmost 20 people were involved in his
OL,7,Ffather's murder, not one has ever been
OL,8,Fbrought to justice.
OL,10,FRyan said: "I don't know who's worse,
OL,11,Fthe British state or the IRA. One side
OL,12,Fis as guilty as the other."
OL,14,FIn a statement a UK government
OL,15,Fspokesperson said: "It would be
OL,16,Finappropriate to comment while
OL,17,Flitigation is ongoing."
OL,19,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,20,FITVX
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/9
